== Grumblr ==

Grumblr is an apploication to post messages to your Tumblr blog
from a GTK-enabled Linux desktop.

=== Licence ===

  New BSD License


=== Requirements: ===

  * Ruby
    http://www.ruby-lang.org/

  * GTK+
    http://www.mozilla.org/

  * LibXml Ruby
    http://libxml.rubyforge.org/

  * REST Client
    http://github.com/archiloque/rest-client


=== Installation ===

  $ sudo gem install grumblr


=== Homepage ===

  http://themactep.com/grumblr/


=== Authors ===

  Paul Philippov <themactep@gmail.com>
